---

<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6 section-alt">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] gap-12 items-start">
      <!-- Left: Title + decorative -->
      <div>
        <span class="font-fira text-xs text-accent tracking-widest uppercase block mb-3">Who I Am</span>
        <h2 class="font-sora text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold section-title">About Me</h2>
        <div class="mt-12 hidden md:block">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-card border border-border">
              <div class="font-sora text-2xl font-bold text-accent">8+</div>
              <div class="font-fira text-xs text-muted mt-1">Blockchain Years</div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-card border border-border">
              <div class="font-sora text-2xl font-bold text-accent">2.5</div>
              <div class="font-fira text-xs text-muted mt-1">Years AI Agents</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Content -->
      <div>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-muted leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg">
          <p>
            I've spent the last decade at the intersection of two fields that are reshaping how we build software:
            <span class="text-text font-medium">artificial intelligence</span> and <span class="text-text font-medium">blockchain</span>.
            What started with building full-stack platforms in 2015
            evolved into smart contracts, DeFi protocols,
            and AI agents that automate complex multi-step workflows.
          </p>
          <p>
            Today I work across the full stack: designing LLM-powered agents with <span class="text-accent">LangChain</span> and <span class="text-accent">CrewAI</span>,
            deploying Solidity contracts for tokenization and DeFi, and shipping web platforms with React and FastAPI.
            As the <span class="text-text font-medium">Founder of Code Minto</span> and a <span class="text-text font-medium">Chainlink Advocate in Ahmedabad</span>,
            I've been part of core teams at <span class="text-text font-medium">Velvet Capital</span>,
            built privacy-first AI systems at <span class="text-text font-medium">Private AI</span>,
            and currently develop AI-driven decentralized applications at <span class="text-text font-medium">Gintonic AI</span>.
          </p>
          <p class="font-medium text-text">
            I care about building things that work — not just things that demo well.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Inline skills preview -->
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {['Solidity', 'LangChain', 'CrewAI', 'FastAPI', 'React.js', 'Web3'].map(skill => (
            <span class="font-fira text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full tag-glow text-muted">{skill}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
